# 📁 Project Structure

```
Customised Virtual File System.cpp
│
├── Boot Block
├── Super Block
├── DILB (Disk Inode List Block)
├── Inode Management
├── UFDT (User File Descriptor Table)
├── File Table
├── File Operations
│   ├── CreateFile()
│   ├── WriteFile()
│   ├── ReadFile()
│   ├── UnlinkFile()
│   └── LsFile()
├── Shell Commands
└── Main Driver
```

---

# 🚀 Compilation

### Linux / macOS

```bash
gcc "Customised Virtual File System.cpp" -o cvfs
./cvfs
```

### Windows (MinGW)

```bash
gcc "Customised Virtual File System.cpp" -o cvfs.exe
cvfs.exe
```

---

# 📊 Project Workflow

```
Start CVFS
      │
      ▼
Initialize Boot Block
      │
      ▼
Initialize Super Block
      │
      ▼
Create DILB
      │
      ▼
Initialize UFDT
      │
      ▼
Launch Shell
      │
      ▼
Execute Commands
      │
      ▼
Terminate
```

---

# ❗ Error Handling

The project provides custom error codes for situations such as:

- Invalid Parameters
- File Already Exists
- File Not Found
- Permission Denied
- No Free Inodes
- Maximum Open Files Reached
- Insufficient Storage Space
- Insufficient Data

